        {
            "title": "山頂私家車自炒反車  女司機自行爬出",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"私家車四輪朝天。fb： 車cam L（香港群組）\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/705c0ee98e036e8994776e7303000f6f/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250320/_2025032014360274619.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">私家車四輪朝天。fb： 車cam L（香港群組）</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今（20日）午1時許，一輛私家車沿山頂道行駛，途至白加道時失控自炒，私家車翻側四輪朝天，女司機自行爬出脫困，她表示輕傷，由救護車送院治理。受事故影響，現場交通擠塞。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4148369/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"私家車四輪朝天。fb： 車cam L（香港群組）\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/379079896d1a37f51cb2c805e4661e0e/2025-03/11_51.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        私家車四輪朝天。fb： 車cam L（香港群組）\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
