            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "華懋西貢WHITESAND COVE最快下周推4伙招標  主打海景戶 示範單位首曝光",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"華懋西貢WHITESAND COVE最快下周推4伙招標  主打海景戶 示範單位首曝光\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/671ab0f543c165e0c0eb998f44f5e808/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250320/_2025032013593948541.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">華懋西貢WHITESAND COVE最快下周推4伙招標  主打海景戶 示範單位首曝光</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>華懋旗下位於西貢白沙灣豪宅項目WHITESAND COVE，今日首度開放示範單位及會所參觀，發展商表示，最快下周招標推售四房海景戶，並指至少推出4伙。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4148277/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/68a694d9e21972307e6f795063d639a5/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-20_at_13_40_07.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4148295/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bfedda6ee5ed30e3ebc39fd6b3479901/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-20_at_13_46_45.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4148294/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e01e22c4513697a3dbd0cf492dda10a9/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-20_at_13_46_45_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4148289/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1479d7906ac07288718e254f42d2d816/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-20_at_13_46_46_3_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>華懋集團銷售總監封海倫表示，項目共提供40個單位，包括5幢分層單位及6幢洋房，戶型涵蓋3房至5房。她指出，項目上月底已上載樓書，本月開放現樓示範單位以來，已錄逾600組客人參觀，其中一半客源來自西貢區，3成為九龍客人，餘下2成則為港島客人，當中內地客佔約兩成。\n\n</p>\n<p>封海倫透露，部署最快下周招標推出3及5座四房海景戶，並指至少會提供4伙招標，面積介乎1,218至1,652方呎。\n\n</p><h2>單位與周邊自然環境融和</h2>\n<p>發展商今日開放一個經改動裝修連傢俬4房示範單位，單位為5座5樓A室，面積1,652方呎，4房4套房大戶，為一層一戶間隔，更設有專屬電梯連接大堂及車庫層，私隱度十足。\n\n</p>\n<p>示範單位設計主題為「Serene Retreat」，靈感源自眼前風光如畫的白沙灣及富有生命力的紅樹林自然生態區，設計師悉心將單位與周邊自然環境融和，連繫室內與外界自然景致。\n\n</p><h2>改動裝修連傢俬4房示範單位：</h2>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4148302/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/51112a25cb2073c2a0ad9c844b9f451a/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-20_at_13_46_43_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4148296/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e2df5f52d93e09bf98576933991830a7/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-20_at_13_46_44_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4148297/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/69357f7db853232f2a48c0c872b3341c/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-20_at_13_46_44_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4148298/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ce26c635432c424209f34b8df9d7e25d/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-20_at_13_46_44.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4148299/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2cdc2128860431ca5ee2e6d2eddc060d/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-20_at_13_46_43_4_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4148301/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a7b58907f50c3bbc6103e91158edb0ff/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-20_at_13_46_43_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4148300/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4368a0441c7923cbc94de7d83a03c743/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-20_at_13_46_43_3_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<p>客飯廳四正實用，並接連50方呎露台 ，飽覽矜罕開揚多層次白沙灣景致，遠眺私人遊艇會風光。貫徹項目採用自然曲線的建築特色，客廳擺放特大的流綫型梳化及絲絨地毯，配上紅色天鵝絨的設計師休閒椅作點綴，典雅與自然融和。\n\n</p>\n<p>飯廳設計同樣貴氣悠然，擺放8人大理石方桌，配以設計獨特及精緻的銀色吊燈，優雅不凡，吊燈名為「The Leaf」與戶外的大自然與紅樹林相呼應。旁邊的掛牆櫃展示了特色花藝和工藝餐具，體現擁抱自然哲學，彰顯非凡品味。\n\n</p>\n<p>單位所有房間均為套房設計，臨海主人套房和書房與客廳同向，呈現銀幕式的白沙灣及紅樹林自然景致；另外兩間套房同樣照顧大戶家庭所需，悉心刻劃各具獨特性的私人空間，分別以灰色綴以粉綠色及粉紅色為主色調，配置書桌及梳妝台，加上玻璃大窗將周圍的翠綠山巒映入室內，閒逸優雅。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4148290/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/be6b6d65f10451c9cbd60cb0dec83ad8/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-20_at_13_46_46_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4148292/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/34da8da8bd8e0b8f83e8f2ca9bfcbf1b/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-20_at_13_46_45_3_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4148291/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6d486a0a3c48e6ad3ea84a349ee1b9ed/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-20_at_13_46_46_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4148293/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8a6c96efcab185a24abd1cd3baace3cd/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-20_at_13_46_45_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
